                            <h1>Payment Integrations</h1>
                            <p>It is no news anymore that technology advances every day, and it has changed or somewhat enhanced all aspects of our daily life. It has been a complete technological overhaul that people are now more comfortable running their everyday transactions or businesses cashless. This is a new realm tech evolution has placed us in. </p>
                            <p>From a hospitality perspective, keeping up with customers’ expectations in this fast-paced, high-tech world can be tricky. Yet, these customers must be afforded that heightened sense of convenience since they are vital to any business organization’s success. </p>
                            <p>As technology evolves, so are guest’s expectations. Taking Uber business as an example, their customers can move around without worrying about payment since everything is handled digitally. Therefore, all customers have to do is have their credit card with them or simply make a wire transfer after the experience is complete. </p>
                        </div>
