            <div class="feature-subpage-box wow fadeInUp">
                <div class="container">
                    <p>Speaking of the hospitality industry, if business owners or managers can afford the same guest experience, it would afford more convenience and increase their revenue, owing to increased booking. Non-cash payments have been around for a while now, and some countries are already on the front foot. Belgium (93%), France (92%), Canada (90%), and UK &amp; Sweden (89%). Other countries like the Asian nation are adopting this new way of payment, and it is just a matter of time before the whole world realizes how rewarding it is. </p>
                    <p>This guide will walk you through what online gateways mean, how your hospitality industry can implement seamless online payments, the 5 best practices to keep your online payment secure, and the importance of online payment integrations.</p>
                </div>
